{
  "stem": "23428.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that happens to be, also, a-- a-- a hospital compound in Auschwitz I, where we were.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was good news.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I think we mingled with the-- whatever was left there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I don't think there were only sick people in Auschwitz I.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There must have been still physicians around because there were people whom we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, so we woke up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We intermingled with them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, of course, I think by that afternoon, there was another call for-- for march.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And actually, I lined up in it, being stupid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but had the-- the-- the-- the instinctive wisdom to call in my famous Prussian manner to the next guard that I had to get in to get something.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these guards were really nervous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Close to nervous breakdown at that point because they know they're just around to be caught.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- so he didn't shoot at me or do anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I ran into the compound and slid into the next bed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, in fact, while I was in the bed, that march went off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that's how I was liberated, essentially.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, there were a few tense days after that, where everybody claimed that the people who couldn't walk were going to be blown up.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we weren't blown up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "At one point, they sent a guy out, like the pigeon in Noah's ark, to find out-- and meanwhile, there was a lot of shooting, of course, around-- whether-- whether it was safe to get out.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, the chap never returned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we stayed in our-- in our beds.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I have no idea how we found nourishment until that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
